{"tid":162931,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"感情重創 寄情湊狗 52歲張曼玉孤伶隱居","createTime":"2017-03-19T15:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T15:57:16.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a72c9ca21bc1377370e002243ab738a8af3a2f8","tid":162931,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"52歲的影后張曼玉（Maggie）對愛情向來勇字放心口，年前被爆與年輕十五年的中英混血Band仔Adrian da Silva行埋，可惜一年感情火速玩完。Maggie近日秘密返港，閉關多時，日前終於出山帶兩隻愛犬到大潭散步。難得到郊外呼吸新鮮空氣，Maggie卻十級戒備，太陽帽、口罩封到冚，免被認出。Maggie曾經歷失婚，被指做第三者、遭撬牆腳，情路崎嶇，到半百之年再面對失戀，枕邊無人，一人兩狗對四面牆，孤伶過活。<br />\n<br />\nBand仔前度唔認數<br />\n<br />\nMaggie一向愛湊鬼，自從同德籍建築師男友Ole分手後一直未有着落，全力醉心玩音樂、學捽碟、剪片，由影后變身音樂狂熱分子，更在音樂圈覓到第二春，14年被爆搭上比自己細十五年的樂隊Audiotraffic前主音及結他手Adrian，二人被影到到淺水灣拍拖放狗，Maggie做埋司機、買靚扒返歸餵嫩仔。<br />\n<br />\nBand仔男友支持下，Maggie學作曲、唱歌，努力投其所愛，熱戀期間，Maggie曾以四千多萬購入小西灣南灣半島高層相連單位，有傳有意作為新愛巢，又有曾在經濟上支持男友的音樂夢。惜拍拖一年就被飛，感情、金錢都付諸流水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/214566_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F214566_2.jpg&h=1d4caefe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/214566_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F214566_3.jpg&h=d1e6ae60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/214566_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F214566_6.jpg&h=9906a004&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdcb1e2b643a3e7eb0648384c9ea8610acd1800b","tid":162931,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"食洋腸臨老比人飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8743d6293006eed7f97b7695e47cc618b724dbe2","tid":162931,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"湊鬼呀嗱<br />\n老版肉便器"},{"pid":"3a8f2391f59980ee8b1d0f614a038ef6ce64dd36","tid":162931,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"全力醉心學捽碟"},{"pid":"fecd2f33df8f3f4576e3200014dc9fe8efff4b29","tid":162931,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"Maggie一向愛湊鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}